  }, "v10"), mdx("p", null, "T\xF4i k\xFD gi\u1EA5y mua , \u0111\xF3ng \u1EA5n v\xE0 t\xECm m\u1EA5y ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ch\u1EE9ng. T\xF4i c\u0169ng c\xE2n b\u1EA1c tr\xEAn c\xE2n. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v11"
