  }, "v13"), mdx("p", null, "Trong khi m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111ang ch\u1EE9ng ki\u1EBFn, t\xF4i b\u1EA3o Ba-r\xFAc r\u1EB1ng, "), mdx("h6", {
