    "id": "v18"
  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\xE0i t\u1ECF l\xF2ng y\xEAu th\u01B0\u01A1ng v\xE0 nh\xE2n t\u1EEB cho h\xE0ng ng\xE0n ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, nh\u01B0ng Ng\xE0i c\u0169ng mang tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t \u0111\u1EBFn cho con ch\xE1u v\xEC t\u1ED9i l\u1ED7i c\u1EE7a cha m\u1EB9 ch\xFAng. L\u1EA1y Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF cao c\u1EA3 v\xE0 v\u0129 \u0111\u1EA1i, danh Ng\xE0i l\xE0 CH\xDAA To\xE0n N\u0103ng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v19"
  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\xE0i d\u1EF1 li\u1EC7u nh\u1EEFng vi\u1EC7c l\u1EDBn. Ng\xE0i bi\u1EBFt h\u1EBFt m\u1ECDi \u0111i\u1EC1u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta l\xE0m, v\xE0 th\u01B0\u1EDFng cho h\u1ECD t\xF9y l\u1ED1i s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD v\xE0 theo \u0111i\u1EC1u h\u1ECD l\xE0m. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v20"
  }, "v20"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\xE0i l\xE0m nhi\u1EC1u ph\xE9p l\u1EA1 v\xE0 nh\u1EEFng vi\u1EC7c di\u1EC7u k\u1EF3 trong x\u1EE9 Ai-c\u1EADp. Ng\xE0i v\u1EABn c\xF2n l\xE0m nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u \u0111\xF3 trong \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 trong c\xE1c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c kh\xE1c cho \u0111\u1EBFn h\xF4m nay. V\xEC th\u1EBF ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ta bi\u1EBFt \u0111\u1EBFn Ng\xE0i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v21"
  }, "v21"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\xE0i mang d\xE2n Ng\xE0i, t\u1EE9c d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en ra kh\u1ECFi Ai-c\u1EADp b\u1EB1ng nh\u1EEFng d\u1EA5u k\u1EF3, ph\xE9p l\u1EA1, quy\u1EC1n n\u0103ng l\u1EDBn lao v\xE0 s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh Ng\xE0i. Ng\xE0i mang \u0111\u1EBFn s\u1EF1 kinh ho\xE0ng cho m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi. "), mdx("h6", {
