  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\xE0i cho h\u1ECD x\u1EE9 n\u1EA7y m\xE0 Ng\xE0i \u0111\xE3 h\u1EE9a cho t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn h\u1ECD t\u1EEB tr\u01B0\u1EDBc, m\u1ED9t v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t ph\xEC nhi\xEAu. "), mdx("h6", {
