  }, "v23"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1ECD \u0111\u1EBFn trong x\u1EE9 n\u1EA7y v\xE0 nh\u1EADn n\xF3 l\xE0m s\u1EA3n nghi\u1EC7p nh\u01B0ng h\u1ECD kh\xF4ng v\xE2ng l\u1EDDi Ng\xE0i v\xE0 \u0111i theo l\u1EDDi gi\xE1o hu\u1EA5n Ng\xE0i. H\u1ECD kh\xF4ng l\xE0m theo m\u1ECDi \u0111i\u1EC1u Ng\xE0i truy\u1EC1n d\u1EB7n. Cho n\xEAn Ng\xE0i khi\u1EBFn nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u kinh khi\u1EBFp n\u1EA7y x\u1EA3y ra cho h\u1ECD. "), mdx("h6", {
