    "id": "v25"
  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "Nh\u01B0ng l\u1EA1y Ch\xFAa l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF, Ng\xE0i b\u1EA3o t\xF4i, 'H\xE3y d\xF9ng b\u1EA1c mua mi\u1EBFng ru\u1ED9ng v\xE0 g\u1ECDi c\xE1c nh\xE2n ch\u1EE9ng \u0111\u1EBFn.' Ng\xE0i b\u1EA3o t\xF4i nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF n\u1EA7y trong khi qu\xE2n Ba-by-l\xF4n s\u1EAFp s\u1EEDa chi\u1EBFm th\xE0nh.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "Sau \u0111\xF3 CH\xDAA ph\xE1n c\xF9ng Gi\xEA-r\xEA-mi r\u1EB1ng: "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v27"
  }, "v27"), mdx("p", null, "\"Ta l\xE0 CH\xDAA, Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF c\u1EE7a m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi tr\xEAn \u0111\u1EA5t. Kh\xF4ng vi\u1EC7c g\xEC ta kh\xF4ng l\xE0m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v28"
  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "Cho n\xEAn CH\xDAA ph\xE1n: Ta s\u1EBD trao th\xE0nh Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem v\xE0o tay qu\xE2n Ba-by-l\xF4n v\xE0 N\xEA-bu-c\xE1t-n\u1EBFt-xa, vua Ba-by-l\xF4n. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi s\u1EBD chi\u1EBFm l\u1EA5y th\xE0nh. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v29"
  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "Qu\xE2n Ba-by-l\xF4n \u0111ang t\u1EA5n c\xF4ng th\xE0nh Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem. H\u1ECD s\u1EAFp v\xE0o th\xE0nh v\xE0 s\u1EBD ph\xF3ng h\u1ECFa \u0111\u1ED1t r\u1EE5i th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 lu\xF4n c\u1EA3 nh\xE0 c\u1EEDa trong \u0111\xF3 m\xE0 d\xE2n ch\xFAng Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem \u0111\xE3 d\xE2ng c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 cho Ba-anh tr\xEAn m\xE1i v\xE0 \u0111\u1ED5 c\xE1c c\u1EE7a l\u1EC5 u\u1ED1ng cho c\xE1c th\u1EA7n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng kh\xE1c \u0111\u1EC3 ch\u1ECDc gi\u1EADn ta. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v30"
  }, "v30"), mdx("p", null, "T\u1EEB khi c\xF2n tr\u1EBB, d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 Giu-\u0111a \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u s\xE1i b\u1EADy. Ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 ch\u1ECDc gi\u1EADn ta b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch b\xE1i l\u1EA1y c\xE1c th\u1EA7n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng do ch\xEDnh tay m\xECnh l\xE0m ra,\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v31"
  }, "v31"), mdx("p", null, "\"T\u1EEB ng\xE0y Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c x\xE2y c\u1EA5t cho \u0111\u1EBFn nay, th\xE0nh n\u1EA7y \u0111\xE3 ch\u1ECDc gi\u1EADn ta, \u0111\u1EBFn n\u1ED7i ta mu\u1ED1n d\u1EB9p n\xF3 \u0111i kh\u1ECFi m\u1EAFt ta. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v32"
  }, "v32"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD ti\xEAu h\u1EE7y n\xF3 v\xEC nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u \xE1c d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 Giu-\u0111a l\xE0m. D\xE2n ch\xFAng, vua, c\xE1c vi\xEAn ch\u1EE9c, c\xE1c th\u1EA7y t\u1EBF l\u1EC5, c\xE1c nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri, to\xE0n d\xE2n Giu-\u0111a v\xE0 d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en \u0111\xE3 ch\u1ECDc gi\u1EADn ta. "), mdx("h6", {
