  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 x\xE2y l\u01B0ng l\u1EA1i c\xF9ng ta, m\xE0 kh\xF4ng x\xE2y m\u1EB7t. Bao l\u1EA7n ta mu\u1ED1n d\u1EA1y ch\xFAng n\xF3 nh\u01B0ng ch\xFAng n\xF3 kh\xF4ng nghe, c\u0169ng kh\xF4ng ch\u1ECBu h\u1ECDc. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v34"
  }, "v34"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u1EB7t nh\u1EEFng th\u1EA7n t\u01B0\u1EE3ng g\u1EDBm ghi\u1EBFc \u1EDF n\u01A1i ta \u0111\xE3 ch\u1ECDn \u0111\u1EC3 th\u1EDD ph\u1EE5ng, khi\u1EBFn cho n\u01A1i \u1EA5y nh\u01A1 nh\u1EDBp. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v35"
  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "Trong thung l\u0169ng B\xEAn-Hin-n\xF4m ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 x\xE2y nh\u1EEFng n\u01A1i th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y Ba-anh \u0111\u1EC3 thi\xEAu con trai con g\xE1i m\xECnh cho th\u1EA7n M\xF4-l\xE9c. Ta kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD b\u1EA3o ch\xFAng l\xE0m nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u g\u1EDBm ghi\u1EBFc nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF. Ta kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD t\u01B0\u1EDFng t\u01B0\u1EE3ng n\u1ED5i r\u1EB1ng ch\xFAng s\u1EBD l\xE0m vi\u1EC7c g\u1EDBm ghi\u1EBFc nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy \u0111\u1EC3 khi\u1EBFn Giu-\u0111a ph\u1EA1m t\u1ED9i.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "Ng\u01B0\u01A1i n\xF3i r\u1EB1ng, \"V\xEC chi\u1EBFn tranh, \u0111\xF3i k\xE9m, d\u1ECBch l\u1EC7, th\xE0nh s\u1EBD b\u1ECB trao v\xE0o tay vua Ba-by-l\xF4n.\" Nh\u01B0ng CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF c\u1EE7a \xCDt-ra-en ph\xE1n nh\u01B0 sau v\u1EC1 Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem: "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "\"Ta \u0111u\u1ED5i d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 Giu-\u0111a ra kh\u1ECFi x\u1EE9 ch\xFAng v\xEC ta n\u1ED5i gi\u1EADn c\xF9ng ch\xFAng. Nh\u01B0ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i ph\u1EA3i bi\u1EBFt r\u1EB1ng ta s\u1EBD s\u1EDBm gom ch\xFAng l\u1EA1i t\u1EEB m\u1ECDi x\u1EE9 m\xE0 ta \u0111\xE3 \u0111\xE0y ch\xFAng \u0111\u1EBFn v\xE0 mang ch\xFAng v\u1EC1 l\u1EA1i t\u1EA1i x\u1EE9 n\u1EA7y \u0111\u1EC3 ch\xFAng s\u1ED1ng b\xECnh y\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v38"
  }, "v38"), mdx("p", null, "D\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 Giu-\u0111a s\u1EBD l\xE0m d\xE2n ta, ta s\u1EBD l\xE0m Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF ch\xFAng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v39"
  }, "v39"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn ch\xFAng mong mu\u1ED1n tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t d\xE2n t\u1ED9c \u0111o\xE0n k\u1EBFt. Ch\xFAng s\u1EBD th\u1EADt l\xF2ng mu\u1ED1n th\u1EDD l\u1EA1y ta su\u1ED1t \u0111\u1EDDi v\xEC \xEDch l\u1EE3i cho ch\xFAng v\xE0 cho con ch\xE1u ch\xFAng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v40"
  }, "v40"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD l\u1EADp giao \u01B0\u1EDBc v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng, giao \u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\xF3 s\u1EBD c\xF2n \u0111\u1EDDi \u0111\u1EDDi. Ta s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD quay m\u1EB7t kh\u1ECFi ch\xFAng; ta s\u1EBD lu\xF4n lu\xF4n l\xE0m l\u1EE3i cho ch\xFAng. Ta s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn ch\xFAng k\xEDnh s\u1EE3 ta th\u1EADt l\xF2ng v\xE0 kh\xF4ng bao gi\u1EDD x\xE2y b\u1ECF ta. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v41"
  }, "v41"), mdx("p", null, "Ta s\u1EBD vui th\xEDch m\xE0 l\xE0m l\u1EE3i cho ch\xFAng. Ta s\u1EBD h\u1EBFt l\xF2ng tr\u1ED3ng ch\xFAng l\u1EA1i trong x\u1EE9 n\u1EA7y v\xE0 khi\u1EBFn ch\xFAng m\u1ECDc l\xEAn.\" "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v42"
  }, "v42"), mdx("p", null, "V\xEC CH\xDAA ph\xE1n nh\u01B0 sau: \"Ta \u0111\xE3 mang \u0111\u1EA1i h\u1ECDa \u0111\u1EBFn cho d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en v\xE0 Giu-\u0111a. C\u0169ng v\u1EADy ta s\u1EBD mang nh\u1EEFng \u0111i\u1EC1u t\u1ED1t l\xE0nh m\xE0 ta \u0111\xE3 h\u1EE9a \u0111\u1EBFn cho ch\xFAng. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v43"
  }, "v43"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i n\xF3i, '\u0110\u1EA5t n\u1EA7y l\xE0 sa m\u1EA1c hoang vu, kh\xF4ng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi hay s\xFAc v\u1EADt n\xE0o \u1EDF. N\xF3 \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c trao cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Ba-by-l\xF4n.' Nh\u01B0ng trong t\u01B0\u01A1ng lai, d\xE2n ch\xFAng s\u1EBD l\u1EA1i mua ru\u1ED9ng trong x\u1EE9 n\u1EA7y. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v44"
  }, "v44"), mdx("p", null, "H\u1ECD s\u1EBD d\xF9ng ti\u1EC1n \u0111\u1EC3 mua ru\u1ED9ng. H\u1ECD s\u1EBD k\xFD t\xEAn v\xE0 \u0111\xF3ng \u1EA5n c\xE1c kh\u1EBF \u01B0\u1EDBc v\xE0 g\u1ECDi nh\xE2n ch\u1EE9ng. H\u1ECD s\u1EBD l\u1EA1i mua ru\u1ED9ng n\u01B0\u01A1ng trong x\u1EE9 B\xEAn-gia-min, v\xF9ng quanh Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem, c\xE1c th\xE0nh c\u1EE7a Giu-\u0111a v\xE0 trong v\xF9ng n\xFAi, v\xF9ng \u0111\u1ED3i ph\xEDa T\xE2y v\xE0 v\xF9ng Nam Giu-\u0111a. Ta s\u1EBD khi\u1EBFn m\u1ECDi v\u1EADt tr\u1EDF l\u1EA1i t\u1ED1t \u0111\u1EB9p cho ch\xFAng nh\u01B0 x\u01B0a,\" CH\xDAA ph\xE1n v\u1EADy."), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
    parentName: "p",
